+* (Physically) Restart X like this:
+  ```shell
+  startx -- -keeptty -nolisten tcp > $HOME/.xorg.log 2>&1
+  ```
+  the error log will be output into `$HOME/.xorg.log`.
+
+* (Virtually) Use [Xephyr](https://wikipedia.org/wiki/Xephyr):
