+notification_preset = {
+    font = "Monospace 10",
+    fg   = "#FFFFFF",
+    bg   = "#000000"
+}
+```
+
+## Output table
+
+Variable | Meaning | Type
+--- | --- | ---
+`widget` | The widget | `wibox.widget.textbox`
+`show` | The notification | function
+
